rComments: Taught Section 2(of 3) in CHM135. Lectures well organized, overview slide at start of each. Emphasis on important content. Enthusiastic, engaging, likeable. In-class examples help. His midterm was easier than the first. Go to lecture, do practice tests and youtube anything confusing and you'll do well in his section.

Very organized lecture slides ; most examples come from the textbook, but reading his slides and filling in the blanks are pretty much enough. Still need to practice a lot to get a grip of the content though.
Talks fast, but gets through important content.
teacherRatingTags: ['Tough grader', 'Get ready to read', 'Gives good feedback']
